channel.title: [PI] Inferno Adze?
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I was wondering on how I can make my inferno Adze to be like Runescapes? Such as: Mining ores, and Cutting Trees, MAYBE, start fires while Woodcutting, but that part isn't really important so I don't care about the Firemaking Part.
I was wondering on what I have to do to make it able to Mine ores and Woodcut though..?
All help is appreciated
